Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.98,0:00:13.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha ha ha ha ha!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.39,0:00:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You're gonna have to\Nwork faster than that
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.10,0:00:17.51,Default,,0,0,0,,if you plan to dig up\Nmy whole village, lass.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.62,0:00:18.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me help.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.22,0:00:19.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.69,0:00:24.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Er, thank you, Rockhoof.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.59,0:00:27.26,Default,,0,0,0,,But we're trying to\Ncarefully preserve
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.46,0:00:29.56,Default,,0,0,0,,every bit of history here.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.83,0:00:34.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Aye, this place is\Nfull of memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.57,0:00:39.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Did I tell you about the time\Nour chieftain knocked down
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.07,0:00:42.87,Default,,0,0,0,,five boulders with the\Nkick of a wee ball?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.21,0:00:46.51,Default,,0,0,0,,OH! STOP THAT!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.45,0:00:49.48,Default,,0,0,0,,But.. that's what this is for.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.68,0:00:51.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe in the past!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.65,0:00:54.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, it belongs in a museum!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.69,0:00:57.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Safe. Preserved. Untouched.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.73,0:01:00.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Bah! Next you'll be saying\NI shouldn't have used
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.36,0:01:01.76,Default,,0,0,0,,the old sweat lodge.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.57,0:01:12.01,Default,,0,0,0,,So you see why Rockhoof isn't\Nan ideal fit for my team.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.41,0:01:17.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Perhaps you could use\Nhis, uh, {\i1}unusual talents{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.31,0:01:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, Professor Fossil!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.98,0:01:21.95,Default,,0,0,0,,We'd be honored to have a Pillar\Nof Equestria on our staff.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.15,0:01:23.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh thank Celestia.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.22,0:01:29.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Blech!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.12,0:01:30.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Agh that apple's made of wood!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.93,0:01:32.56,Default,,0,0,0,,What a horrible trick to play!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.13,0:01:39.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm.  Has anypony seen my\Ndecorative centerpieces?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.23,0:01:40.33,Default,,0,0,0,,They were right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.10,0:01:42.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Good luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.45,0:02:26.72,Default,,0,0,0,,So join me in welcoming\NProfessor Rockhoof
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.81,0:02:28.08,Default,,0,0,0,,to our faculty!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.32,0:02:34.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, thank you all.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.49,0:02:38.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I know I'm new to your world,\Nbut there's one thing I learned
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.23,0:02:42.17,Default,,0,0,0,,when I saved my village from\Na rushing river of hot lava...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.66,0:02:46.83,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing you can't do\Nwith hard work... and a shovel!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.01,0:02:54.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Except maybe stand on stage..
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.21,0:03:02.74,Default,,0,0,0,,So, um, everycreature\Ndismissed!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.05,0:03:04.82,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll... see you in class!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.35,0:03:08.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You think that new\Npony is gonna be
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.19,0:03:10.09,Default,,0,0,0,,the weirdest\Nteacher at school?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.19,0:03:12.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Or just one of the weirdest?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.16,0:03:13.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Yona like new teacher!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.06,0:03:16.13,Default,,0,0,0,,He big, like yak!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.43,0:03:18.43,Default,,0,0,0,,And he smashes\Nthings like a yak.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.73,0:03:20.40,Default,,0,0,0,,He smells like a yak...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.80,0:03:23.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes! He perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.87,0:03:26.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Guys, he's one\Nof the Pillars!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.27,0:03:28.74,Default,,0,0,0,,He's like...\NPony history!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.84,0:03:30.71,Default,,0,0,0,,HELLO CLASS!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.28,0:03:34.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.82,0:03:38.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm er.. your new "Theory and\NDefense of Friendship" teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.29,0:03:41.69,Default,,0,0,0,,But I haven't had\Na chance to look
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.79,0:03:43.46,Default,,0,0,0,,at Headmare\NTwilight's notes yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.26,0:03:45.43,Default,,0,0,0,,What have you all\Nbeen learning?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.73,0:03:48.50,Default,,0,0,0,,We just studied all about how\NPrincess Celestia and Luna
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.80,0:03:51.43,Default,,0,0,0,,used a spell to trap\NDiscord in stone sleep
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.53,0:03:52.66,Default,,0,0,0,,for hundreds of moons.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.17,0:03:54.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, hohoho...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.97,0:03:57.50,Default,,0,0,0,,so it's a class\Nabout stories, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.70,0:03:59.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Stories, yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.27,0:04:01.44,Default,,0,0,0,,And we never, ever,\Never get homework.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.74,0:04:04.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Good! The best way to\Nteach colts and fillies
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.48,0:04:06.18,Default,,0,0,0,,is by experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.58,0:04:11.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Like the time I was in the woods\Nand ran across an Ursa Major.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.65,0:04:12.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Really!?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.62,0:04:13.85,Default,,0,0,0,,We're not doing\Nthat, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.15,0:04:15.95,Default,,0,0,0,,You fight Ursa Major?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.46,0:04:17.89,Default,,0,0,0,,All alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.99,0:04:20.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Aye! And I\Ndefeated her too!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.26,0:04:23.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Now this, I'm interested in.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.73,0:04:25.60,Default,,0,0,0,,How Professor Rockhoof win?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.10,0:04:29.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that's quite a tale.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.80,0:04:33.20,Default,,0,0,0,,From what Professor Fossil said,\Nit sounds like Rockhoof
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.31,0:04:35.54,Default,,0,0,0,,just hasn't settled into\Nmodern times yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.64,0:04:37.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Our school is the\Nperfect place for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.91,0:04:39.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Plus, we get a new teacher!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.71,0:04:42.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Heh. This may be the fastest\Nfriendship problem
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.35,0:04:43.25,Default,,0,0,0,,you ever solved.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.95,0:04:49.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Dodge! Thrust! Shovel Leap!\NShovel Throw!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.76,0:04:54.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Shovel Whack!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.16,0:04:57.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Now you lot be the Ursa Major.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.66,0:04:59.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Lotsa growling, mind!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.24,0:05:03.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha ha ha ha!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.51,0:05:08.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe classrooms were less\Nbreakable in the old days?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.41,0:05:11.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Ooh ooh ooh! What\Nhappened next?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.78,0:05:15.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Heh heh. The huge beastie jumped\Nout of the moonlit mist,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.25,0:05:19.12,Default,,0,0,0,,her fearsome fangs at my throat!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.62,0:05:20.75,Default,,0,0,0,,But I rolled clear!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.09,0:05:23.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Then what!?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.02,0:05:28.09,Default,,0,0,0,,She backed me up against\Na wall, ready to pounce!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.10,0:05:32.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I looked at her...\Nshe looked at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.73,0:05:33.63,Default,,0,0,0,,And I say--
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.73,0:05:34.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh Professor\NRockhoof?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.04,0:05:35.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Nope, guess again!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.24,0:05:37.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Ahem. Oops.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.84,0:05:39.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry to interrupt.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.27,0:05:42.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Class, why don't we go ahead\Nand take lunch early today?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.58,0:05:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Rockhoof, can we\Ntake a walk outside?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.58,0:05:51.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Our school is about finding\Nyour own special way to teach.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.95,0:05:55.75,Default,,0,0,0,,And we can already tell\Nyou're a smash with the class!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.16,0:06:00.26,Default,,0,0,0,,But maybe you could do a little\Nless smashing in the classroom?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.66,0:06:03.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry about that. I did get\Na bit carried away.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.00,0:06:06.80,Default,,0,0,0,,The students were so\Ninterested in my tale!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.17,0:06:11.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I know it's a big change,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.81,0:06:13.38,Default,,0,0,0,,but I think you're\Ngonna fit in just--
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.28,0:06:19.61,Default,,0,0,0,,FIRE!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.71,0:06:20.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Rockhoof, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.91,0:06:22.61,Default,,0,0,0,,No time! The building's ablaze!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.72,0:06:24.32,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to get everypony out!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.42,0:06:26.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Professor Rockhoof\Nbest teacher ever!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.82,0:06:29.09,Default,,0,0,0,,[sigh] Day cannot get better!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.56,0:06:32.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's get you\Noutside, wee ones!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.49,0:06:35.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Day just got better!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.28,0:06:37.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.73,0:06:38.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Ally-Oop!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.20,0:06:41.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Rockhoof!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.40,0:06:42.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing!?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.80,0:06:43.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Saving the school!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.68,0:06:51.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Just like fighting a volcano\Nin the good old days!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.32,0:06:56.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Would somepony\Nkindly explain
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.18,0:06:58.25,Default,,0,0,0,,what is the meaning\Nof all this water?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.35,0:07:01.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not sure, but I\Nthink it's "Surf's up!"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.46,0:07:03.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Wheeeeee! Cowabunga!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.32,0:07:04.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, Rarity.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.36,0:07:06.49,Default,,0,0,0,,But I had to put out\Nthe raging inferno!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.99,0:07:08.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Inferno? Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.96,0:07:10.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you not see the\Nsmoke and flame?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.10,0:07:12.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that was us.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.20,0:07:14.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Y'know, DRAGONS?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.90,0:07:17.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Having a firebreathing\Ncompetition?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.34,0:07:19.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You... what?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.51,0:07:21.01,Default,,0,0,0,,They do it all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.21,0:07:23.04,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what we were\Ntrying to tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.14,0:07:25.67,Default,,0,0,0,,We know you're used to\Nbeing a hero, Rockhoof.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.08,0:07:29.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Only... what we need\Nhere is a teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.15,0:07:33.62,Default,,0,0,0,,One who doesn't ruin an entire\Nclass's friendship quilts!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.72,0:07:37.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know how hard it is to\Nstitch a pineapple pattern!?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.12,0:07:41.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh. My deepest apologies.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.50,0:07:43.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not used to\Nliving with dragons.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.83,0:07:46.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Or much else in\Nthis modern time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.63,0:07:48.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Professor Fossil\Nmade it clear
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.37,0:07:50.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not welcome back\Nin my old village.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.24,0:07:53.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Seems I don't\Nbelong here either.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.18,0:07:58.81,Default,,0,0,0,,WHEEEE!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.92,0:08:06.42,Default,,0,0,0,,So apparently,\Nfinding Rockhoof a new job
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.52,0:08:08.32,Default,,0,0,0,,is a lot harder than we thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.42,0:08:10.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Has anypony had any luck?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.79,0:08:13.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh uh. Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.73,0:08:18.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought you were gonna try\Nhim out at the post office.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.53,0:08:19.36,Default,,0,0,0,,We did.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.17,0:08:25.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know where I can\Nfind Cranky Doodle Donkey?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.11,0:08:27.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I need to deliver his medicine!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.31,0:08:31.08,Default,,0,0,0,,He has a rash in a very\Nembarrassing place!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.29,0:08:40.82,Default,,0,0,0,,[shudder] I did not\Nneed to hear that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.32,0:08:44.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep! Rockhoof's time\Nas a spa masseuse
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.46,0:08:45.99,Default,,0,0,0,,didn't work out either.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.49,0:08:50.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Now just let me know if\Nthis is too much PRESSURE.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.17,0:08:59.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, at least Rockhoof's\Nreally strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.47,0:09:02.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe we could find him a\Njob carrying heavy stuff?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.08,0:09:04.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I tried that already!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.65,0:09:07.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Zecora needed somepony to\Nhelp her get supplies, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.25,0:09:13.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I know you said you only\Nneeded a few leaves,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.89,0:09:15.69,Default,,0,0,0,,but I figured why not\Nbring you the whole thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.66,0:09:23.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, how horrid.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.40,0:09:25.60,Default,,0,0,0,,None of the other Pillars\Nseem to be having trouble
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.70,0:09:27.47,Default,,0,0,0,,fitting in to the modern world.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.87,0:09:30.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Then maybe they can show\NRockhoof how they did it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.74,0:09:32.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Get him used to\Nlivin' in this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.07,0:09:34.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Great idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.46,0:09:36.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Rockhoof's old friends\Nwould be happy to help.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.54,0:09:38.31,Default,,0,0,0,,And I bet he'd\Nlove to visit them.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.42,0:09:43.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmph.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.12,0:09:47.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Even Canterlot looks\Ndifferent from the old days.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.25,0:09:50.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Aw, I'm sure once you see\Nyour ol' pal Flash Magnus,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.86,0:09:52.26,Default,,0,0,0,,you'll feel right at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.86,0:09:56.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Trot, 2, 3, 4!\NTrot, 2, 3, 4!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.86,0:09:58.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep it lively, rookies!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.57,0:10:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Visitors on site!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.30,0:10:03.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Company, halt!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.81,0:10:09.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Rockhoof, you old\Nditch-digger you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.68,0:10:12.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Flash Magnus, as I\Nlive and breathe!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.98,0:10:14.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this your squadron?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.95,0:10:17.78,Default,,0,0,0,,After we got out of limbo, I\Nwent looking for work for a pony
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.88,0:10:19.68,Default,,0,0,0,,with experience in\Nthe Royal Legion.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.99,0:10:22.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Once a soldier,\Nalways a soldier.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.69,0:10:25.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Princess Celestia was happy to\Nfind a new drill sergeant
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.19,0:10:26.36,Default,,0,0,0,,for her Guard!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.46,0:10:28.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.. that's great.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.10,0:10:32.77,Default,,0,0,0,,She really put you in a\Njob that big... so soon?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.17,0:10:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, this is nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.90,0:10:36.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You should see what\NMistmane is up to.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.51,0:10:42.98,Default,,0,0,0,,They made {\i1}you{\i0} the Royal\NLandscape Artist
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.08,0:10:44.71,Default,,0,0,0,,for the Crystal Empire?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.01,0:10:45.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.95,0:10:47.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Your work is\Nbeautiful!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.12,0:10:49.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.92,0:10:52.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never worked\Nwith crystal before,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.52,0:10:56.32,Default,,0,0,0,,but in my heart, I know\NI'm where I belong.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.12,0:10:59.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You always could find\Nthe beauty in things.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.93,0:11:03.70,Default,,0,0,0,,But there's not much demand for\Nshovel ponies like me nowadays.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.87,0:11:06.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't give up hope!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.80,0:11:08.43,Default,,0,0,0,,See Somnambula.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.54,0:11:11.31,Default,,0,0,0,,She'll help you\Nfind your purpose.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.07,0:11:16.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Somnambula's a\Nmotivational speaker.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.51,0:11:18.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Bet they didn't even have\Nthose back in your time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.15,0:11:20.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Because we didn't\Nneed them.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.91,0:11:22.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Ponies knew what to\Ndo with their lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.08,0:11:29.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Focus on my voice, and feel\Nyourself unlock your potential.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.96,0:11:43.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Imagine everything that\Ntroubles you as one big cloud.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.64,0:11:46.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Now let it float away.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.31,0:11:49.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You are relaxed.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.31,0:11:52.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Free to do anything you wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.92,0:12:00.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Guess he wished he\Ncould take a nap?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.16,0:12:04.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Rockhoof: Mage Meadowbrook!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.59,0:12:07.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Your home looks just the\Nsame as the old days.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.73,0:12:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Wish I could say\Nthe same for mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.80,0:12:13.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I've had to\Nexpand my clinic a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.53,0:12:16.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Many creatures need healing\Nin this modern world.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.97,0:12:20.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! Looks like you\Ncould use some too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.57,0:12:23.07,Default,,0,0,0,,What's got you\Nheartsick, Rockhoof?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.75,0:12:29.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Thing is, I can't do\Nmy old job like Flash.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.15,0:12:30.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Or adapt like Mistmane.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.95,0:12:33.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Or succeed at something\Nnew like Somnambula.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.89,0:12:35.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Or go home, like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.32,0:12:37.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Give it time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.54,0:12:40.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Even Starswirl's still\Nlearning about friendship...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.16,0:12:41.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Applejack: Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.23,0:12:45.20,Default,,0,0,0,,And I bet Stygian took\Nplenty of time to fit in.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.30,0:12:46.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, look what I found!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.27,0:12:49.77,Default,,0,0,0,,"Me and My Shadow,"\Nthe third hit novel
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.87,0:12:51.74,Default,,0,0,0,,by former villain Stygian!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.84,0:12:53.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm impressed! He's\Nreally thriving!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.64,0:12:58.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Rockhoof? Where are\Nyou going?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.91,0:12:59.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.06,0:13:02.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe I just don't belong\Nin this modern world.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.55,0:13:08.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Now this here is a\Nright mash of apples.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.52,0:13:10.69,Default,,0,0,0,,'Stead of solving\NRockhoof's problem,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.79,0:13:12.56,Default,,0,0,0,,we made him feel even worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.96,0:13:15.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll tell you the\Nreal problem here!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.30,0:13:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,,We haven't given Rockhoof the\Nchance to be who he really is.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.33,0:13:21.87,Default,,0,0,0,,A pony with a metal shovel\Nand a heart of gold?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.37,0:13:24.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Tch. A hero!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.40,0:13:28.34,Default,,0,0,0,,What we need to do is find him\Na job that's as epic as he is!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.94,0:13:32.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm. I might know\Njust the thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.61,0:13:37.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Rockhoof: I'm honored to serve\Nin the Hippogriff Navy,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.52,0:13:38.69,Default,,0,0,0,,General Seaspray.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.99,0:13:41.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I promise I'll prove my worth.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.29,0:13:43.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Think nothing of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.86,0:13:47.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I know how hard it is\Nto adapt to a new home.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.16,0:13:49.96,Default,,0,0,0,,After our many years\Nbelow the waves,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.16,0:13:53.23,Default,,0,0,0,,land customs seemed strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.43,0:13:56.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Like you didn't fit in, no\Nmatter how hard you tried?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.37,0:13:59.51,Default,,0,0,0,,As though the world had\Nmoved on without us.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.81,0:14:01.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Never fear, Rockhoof!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.47,0:14:07.78,Default,,0,0,0,,We shall be as brothers in this\Nbright future above the waves.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.18,0:14:10.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, why do the\NHippogriffs need ships
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.05,0:14:12.85,Default,,0,0,0,,if they can turn\Ninto seaponies?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.05,0:14:14.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe they just like cruises?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.29,0:14:16.04,Default,,0,0,0,,General!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.24,0:14:18.89,Default,,0,0,0,,The fog's too thick to see\Nour way out of the harbor!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.76,0:14:23.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Heave to, swabbies!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.16,0:14:28.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Halt the ship and hold\Nher till the fog passes!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.47,0:14:30.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, General!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.54,0:14:33.21,Default,,0,0,0,,We can navigate the same way\Nmy Coltic ancestors traveled
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.31,0:14:37.31,Default,,0,0,0,,through the Selkie Mists!\NWe'll look to the stars!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.61,0:14:39.24,Default,,0,0,0,,There in the\Nnorthwest sky
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.35,0:14:41.92,Default,,0,0,0,,is the constellation\Nfor O'Bridle's Pelt!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.42,0:14:44.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Steer the ship toward that!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.82,0:14:46.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You heard the pony, crew!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.69,0:14:48.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Make full sail!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.46,0:14:55.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeehaw! Rockhoof did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.16,0:14:59.33,Default,,0,0,0,,But... I don't understand!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.43,0:15:01.90,Default,,0,0,0,,The stars have always\Nsteered me true!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.10,0:15:05.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no. Stars can move\Nslowly over time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.27,0:15:08.14,Default,,0,0,0,,They must look different now\Nthan over a thousand years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.74,0:15:11.91,Default,,0,0,0,,It was an honor serving\Nwith you, Rockhoof.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.21,0:15:16.91,Default,,0,0,0,,But it seems our paths lie\Nin different directions.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.36,0:15:24.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, mistakes happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.42,0:15:26.35,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll think of something\Nelse for you to do!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.96,0:15:29.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, there's no need, lass.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.13,0:15:31.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I already know what\NI want to do next.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.56,0:15:32.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Really? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.50,0:15:35.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard there's a\Nstatue spell
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.44,0:15:37.87,Default,,0,0,0,,that sends creatures\Ninto stone sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.17,0:15:39.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I want you to cast it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.27,0:15:41.70,Default,,0,0,0,,On me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.95,0:15:48.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Twilight: No!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.68,0:15:49.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Rockhoof: Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.45,0:15:50.88,Default,,0,0,0,,-No!\N-Aye!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.79,0:15:53.39,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.49,0:15:54.32,Default,,0,0,0,,AYE!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.52,0:15:55.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.56,0:15:57.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Need me to help you\Ndecide something?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.59,0:16:01.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Rockhoof wants me to cast a\Nspell to turn him into a statue.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.16,0:16:03.79,Default,,0,0,0,,The answer is no.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.90,0:16:07.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it should be "aye", because\NI wouldn't even be here
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.47,0:16:08.90,Default,,0,0,0,,to be turned into a statue
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.00,0:16:12.04,Default,,0,0,0,,if Twilight hadn't cast a\Nspell in the first place!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.11,0:16:16.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa. I thought you were\Narguing over ice cream flavors.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.68,0:16:18.55,Default,,0,0,0,,The answer is still no!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.65,0:16:20.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Why would you want to\Nbe turned into stone?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.95,0:16:23.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I'm a relic\Nof a bygone age.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.08,0:16:25.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I belong in a museum.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.72,0:16:26.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.52,0:16:27.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Preserved.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.42,0:16:28.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Untouched.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.12,0:16:30.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't belong in this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.92,0:16:32.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It's up to you to\Nmake that right!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.26,0:16:35.13,Default,,0,0,0,,But there has to\Nbe a better way!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.23,0:16:37.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Twilight, please understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.36,0:16:39.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to be remembered\Nas the hero I was.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.93,0:16:42.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Not the disappointment\NI've become.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.30,0:16:43.40,Default,,0,0,0,,But you're not!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.70,0:16:44.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Rockhoof, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.14,0:16:48.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Spike, can you teach\Nmy class today?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.84,0:16:51.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Er, you're not really going to\Nturn him to stone, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.15,0:16:53.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Only because it's temporary.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.98,0:16:55.85,Default,,0,0,0,,As soon as I think\Nof a new solution,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.95,0:16:57.35,Default,,0,0,0,,we'll wake Rockhoof up.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.45,0:17:01.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I KNOW he has more to offer the\Nworld as a pony than a statue.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.76,0:17:05.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you hear Rockhoof caught all\Nthe bees in the Everfree Forest,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.33,0:17:06.93,Default,,0,0,0,,and gave 'em to\NZecora as a gift?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.13,0:17:10.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow! Terramar said Rockhoof\Ncalled down the stars
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.30,0:17:12.53,Default,,0,0,0,,and sunk the whole\NHippogriff navy!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.63,0:17:15.46,Default,,0,0,0,,He's definitely weird.\NBut in a fun way.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.67,0:17:17.87,Default,,0,0,0,,You never know what's\Ngonna happen next with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.17,0:17:20.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Professor Rockhoof best pony!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.11,0:17:22.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, class.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.84,0:17:25.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome to the Theory and\NDefense of Friendship.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.55,0:17:26.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Another sub?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.68,0:17:29.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me start by telling\Nyou we don't get homework,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.62,0:17:31.52,Default,,0,0,0,,and we only do field trips.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.22,0:17:33.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, nice try.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.85,0:17:35.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Er, Twilight sent me to tell\Nyou she won't be in today
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.99,0:17:38.86,Default,,0,0,0,,'cause she has to cast a stone\Nsleep spell on Rockhoof.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.69,0:17:42.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Like Discord? But why!?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.70,0:17:44.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Rockhoof isn't a bad guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.16,0:17:45.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.57,0:17:49.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Your instructions are\Nto write an essay on
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.30,0:17:51.53,Default,,0,0,0,,"Heroism: And What It\NMeans To You."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.84,0:17:53.01,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.41,0:17:54.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.44,0:17:55.91,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't have to\Nbe a long essay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.98,0:18:00.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe like.. this?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.28,0:18:02.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Or on three legs... Hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.82,0:18:07.02,Default,,0,0,0,,What will give the wee birds\Nfewer places to uh, decorate?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.12,0:18:08.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Yona: Professor Rockhoof!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.49,0:18:10.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Dragon said you want\Nto turn into stone!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.59,0:18:14.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Yona not believe it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.33,0:18:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Aye, I'm afraid it's true, lass.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.70,0:18:21.50,Default,,0,0,0,,But... Pony need finish\NUrsa Major story for class!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.00,0:18:25.14,Default,,0,0,0,,It's sweet of you to try\Nto get me to stay, Yona.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.44,0:18:28.94,Default,,0,0,0,,But... I'm afraid old\Nstories like mine
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.14,0:18:31.91,Default,,0,0,0,,aren't worth anything\Nin this day and age.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.11,0:18:35.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine! If Pony no want\Ntell Yona story,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.22,0:18:37.45,Default,,0,0,0,,then Yona tell Pony story!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.79,0:18:40.99,Default,,0,0,0,,From class report!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.09,0:18:44.26,Default,,0,0,0,,"When Yona come to Pony\Nschool, Yona not fit in.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.56,0:18:46.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Pony ways strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.23,0:18:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,But Yona find friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.19,0:18:50.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Yona meet Professor Rockhoof.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.83,0:18:53.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Pony brave and strong as Yak!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.90,0:18:55.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Not afraid! Hero!"
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.24,0:18:57.54,Default,,0,0,0,,When Yona grow up,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.64,0:19:01.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Yona want to be just like\NProfessor Rockhoof!"
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.37,0:19:05.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Well.... since you went\Nto the trouble
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.54,0:19:08.48,Default,,0,0,0,,of writing something\Nthat nice, I suppose
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.58,0:19:11.18,Default,,0,0,0,,the least I could do is tell\Nyou the rest of the story.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.82,0:19:16.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Yona tell whole school\NRockhoof is best!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.92,0:19:18.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Now ALL want to hear story!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.63,0:19:23.56,Default,,0,0,0,,OK. I have the spell,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.86,0:19:26.39,Default,,0,0,0,,but will you please\Nreconsider. Rockhoof!?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.50,0:19:29.67,Default,,0,0,0,,The Ursa Major tried to\Ngrab me by the gullet!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.87,0:19:31.14,Default,,0,0,0,,But I ducked her claws!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.01,0:19:36.31,Default,,0,0,0,,She had me cornered.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.41,0:19:39.14,Default,,0,0,0,,So I look at her..\Nshe looks at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.28,0:19:46.25,Default,,0,0,0,,And I say, "Sorry you won't be\Nhaving any dinner tonight, lass!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.35,0:19:49.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Guess you'll just have\Nto.. grin and bear it!"
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.96,0:19:55.33,Default,,0,0,0,,And then I tossed her away with\Nmy shovel, high into the sky!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.73,0:19:59.67,Default,,0,0,0,,And she's been a constellation\Nup there ever since.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.77,0:20:00.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Or so I'm told.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.23,0:20:03.63,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's the end of my story.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.04,0:20:08.08,Default,,0,0,0,,One more story!\NOne more story!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.17,0:20:10.37,Default,,0,0,0,,No no. Thank you\Nfor listening.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.48,0:20:12.31,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's time to say good-bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.08,0:20:14.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.98,0:20:17.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You said there wasn't anything\Nin this time you were good at.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.98,0:20:19.78,Default,,0,0,0,,What about telling stories?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.62,0:20:23.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It was just a tall tale...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.12,0:20:26.39,Default,,0,0,0,,One that captured the\Nhearts and imagination
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.49,0:20:28.09,Default,,0,0,0,,of everycreature here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.79,0:20:31.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Plus pony story super fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.83,0:20:37.86,Default,,0,0,0,,As the Princess of Friendship,\NI'd like to appoint you
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.07,0:20:40.94,Default,,0,0,0,,as Equestria's official\NKeeper of Tales!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.84,0:20:43.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.71,0:20:44.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Meh.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.84,0:20:47.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I uh.... That's\Nvery kind of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.88,0:20:50.75,Default,,0,0,0,,But I still think these old\Nbones are more suited
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.85,0:20:52.52,Default,,0,0,0,,to a museum display.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.82,0:20:55.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You are a living\Nrecord of our history.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.66,0:20:58.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Your stories can inspire and\Nteach generations to come!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.13,0:21:01.70,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're a statue,\Nthat's all lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.40,0:21:05.70,Default,,0,0,0,,But will I ever really\Nbelong in your world?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.10,0:21:07.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Rockhoof Yona's friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.77,0:21:09.17,Default,,0,0,0,,So Rockhoof belongs.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.07,0:21:14.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, that reminds\Nme of another story...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.24,0:21:20.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Once there was a small Yak that\Nknew more than a great hero.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.71,0:21:23.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, don't forget the\Ndragons in this one!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.02,0:21:25.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Aye, there were dragons!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.55,0:21:27.12,Default,,0,0,0,,And ponies.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.42,0:21:29.35,Default,,0,0,0,,And plenty of hippogriffs...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.46,0:21:32.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Plus a changeling and\Na griffon that flew...
